orders  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  2  ¦  999.99  ¦  pending  𝄀
orders  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  3  ¦  999.99  ¦  pending  𝄀
orders_cloned  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  4  ¦  400.00  ¦  branch_only
data branch merge orders_cloned into orders;
data branch diff orders_cloned against orders;
➤ diff orders_cloned against orders[12,0,0]  ¦  flag[12,0,0]  ¦  id[4,0,0]  ¦  price[3,-1,0]  ¦  status[12,0,0]  𝄀
orders  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  1  ¦  999.99  ¦  pending  𝄀
orders  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  2  ¦  999.99  ¦  pending  𝄀
orders  ¦  UPDATE  ¦  3  ¦  999.99  ¦  pending
select * from orders order by id;
